* netclasses MUST be installed before installation *

Installation Instructions:

1. First you must install TalkSoupBundles
 andy ~/TalkSoup $ cd TalkSoupBundles
 andy ~/TalkSoup/TalkSoupBundles $ make
 andy ~/TalkSoup/TalkSoupBundles $ su -c 'make install'

2. Now you must install TalkSoup, go back to the head source directory.
 andy ~/TalkSoup $ make
 andy ~/TalkSoup/TalkSoupBundles $ su -c 'make install'
	
3. Run TalkSoup
 andy ~ $ gopen TalkSoup.app

Enjoy!

See the README and FAQ for more usage instructions

